{"tid":2458622,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"交通警被捕兼停職 申請遮仔會貸款涉詐騙 明日上午觀塘法院提堂","createTime":"2021-03-23T14:24:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T15:53:47.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c6616f5a97e0dc25fd423e48728e49dd71bc8faa","tid":2458622,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T14:24:15.000Z","msg":"警方今日（23日）晚上9時許表示，東九龍重案組於2月18日在沙頭角區拘捕一名38歲男警員，涉嫌向俗稱「遮仔會」的警察儲蓄互助社申請貸款時，隱瞞財務狀況。據了解，涉事警員隸屬東九龍總區交通部，懷疑向遮仔會貸款前，隱瞞有從坊間公司貸款狀況。<br />\n<br />\n被捕男警已被控三項「詐騙」罪，將於明日（24日）上午於觀塘裁判法院提堂。該名警務人員已被停職。<br />\n<br />\n警察儲蓄互助社因會徽緣故俗稱「遮仔會」，於1981年註冊成立，主要為在職和退休警員提供存貸服務。遮仔會設有由15名現職和退休警務人員組成的董事會，負責處理入社申請、釐定貸款利率、建議派發股息、運用本社資金投資等。遮仔會另設貸款委員會、監察委員會及教育委員會，分別負責審批貸款、審查賬目、宣傳等工作。<br />\n<br />\n警務處副處長（行動）蕭澤頤亦曾擔任遮仔會社長，他於2017年1月獲晉升至助理處長後，5月以「公事繁忙」為由辭任社長一職；現任社長為投訴及內部調查科總警司麥衛文。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210323/HBBU6RUEUNB53DHNN53GUYSIQE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210323%2FHBBU6RUEUNB53DHNN53GUYSIQE%2F&d=9ZLePgUN12BIej1hBtk97bccVloK1XwbfTGMhSGe0oU%3D&h=da42ad4b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2F20210323%2FHBBU6RUEUNB53DHNN53GUYSIQE%2F&h=06fb0038\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/breaking/20210323/HBBU6RUEUNB53DHNN53GUYSIQE/</a>"},{"pid":"743aea6646ef38e0b5e085c5c8e52c6d2ecfe03c","tid":2458622,"uid":65888,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T14:25:51.000Z","msg":"Lm撤控<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b07fcec94c0a9c994d7d980bd1d048dcbcc495c1","tid":2458622,"uid":23635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"743aea6646ef38e0b5e085c5c8e52c6d2ecfe03c","tid":2458622,"uid":65888,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T14:25:51.000Z","msg":"Lm撤控<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T14:28:00.000Z","msg":"呃自己友錢喎，點會咁易？"},{"pid":"695b83b08caf317ab29ac115b26a7d31e4b1fdc9","tid":2458622,"uid":21470,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T14:29:48.000Z","msg":"遮仔會 D 錢係共產黨架，打土豪"},{"pid":"cfc7ccb2a18afa0c701d70c7e40394b80aefd733","tid":2458622,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T14:31:17.000Z","msg":"嫖賭飲吹樣樣齊"},{"pid":"ecf9771286b03d4e6afe9508a3544290a9f091bd","tid":2458622,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T14:39:55.000Z","msg":"黑保護傘會"},{"pid":"31653a295ba94219388b0aee5877330291296212","tid":2458622,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T14:41:19.000Z","msg":"邊間做債務重組好？就想死<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2442556\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2442556</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0144df9bc59b5aa478f426b5da2b7e6f2054d465","tid":2458622,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T14:42:02.000Z","msg":"&rsquo;合法&lsquo;洗黑錢組織？<br />\n<br />\n星火好無辜"},{"pid":"70ff761b7a6d9f5ec6e718d718bdbee37dc373de","tid":2458622,"uid":136140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T14:43:51.000Z","msg":"咁大個會罩住都可以搞到咁折墮"},{"pid":"8de055aca34275ef0ee142e07bda95b8114159a7","tid":2458622,"uid":56900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-23T15:53:47.000Z","msg":"又係黑暴搞到專心唔到 人有錯漏"}]}